<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 02 at 7:45PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT AS
SNOW INTENSITY BEGINS TO WANE...
WEATHER...
* Light snow continues into early tonight before tapering off
around/after midnight.
* Additional accumulations of an inch or less before snow comes
to an end.
* Temperatures in the 20s falling into the upper teens tonight.
IMPACTS...
* Hazardous driving conditions as untreated roads remain snow
covered.
&amp;&amp;
PRECAUTIONARY/PREPAREDNESS ACTIONS...
* Motorists are urged to use caution and account for the
hazardous driving conditions by allowing extra time.
* Prepare, plan and stay informed. Visit http://go.usa.gov/c7kkP</description>
